On Escalation Ticket # 00413468 the new comment has been added: Augustina Sidor:

@Flaviu Moldovan in this case, I think the problem is not related to the vulnerability patch. 
It's more related to the devices and rights set at the group level. 
In the last weeks, two more issues were raised regarding the device rights set at the group level after upgrading the server to 5.9.3.0.

In this case, please follow the procedure from this ticket #340075 

[DevOps CommentId:10516187]
